        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Ending Critical Race Theory in D.C. Public Schools Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits any employee of the District of Columbia Public Schools or the District of Columbia Public Charter Schools from compelling a teacher or student to adopt, affirm, adhere to, or profess ideas that promote race or sex stereotyping or scapegoating.</p>]]>
        </text>
